{{Infobox journal | title = Journal of Health Politics, Policy and Law | cover = | caption = | former_name = <!-- or |former_names= --> | abbreviation = J. Health Politics Policy Law | bluebook = J. Health Pol. Pol'y & L. | discipline = [[Health policy]], [[health law]] | peer-reviewed = | language = English | editor = Eric M. Patashnik | publisher = [[Duke University Press]] | country = | history = 1976-present | frequency = Bimonthly | openaccess = | license = | impact = 1.373 | impact-year = 2014 | ISSNlabel = | ISSN = 0361-6878 | eISSN = 1527-1927 | CODEN = JHPLDN | JSTOR = | LCCN = | OCLC = 2115780 | website = http://jhppl.dukejournals.org/ | link1 = http://jhppl.dukejournals.org/content/current | link1-name = Online access | link2 = http://jhppl.dukejournals.org/content/by/year | link2-name = Online archive | boxwidth = }} The '''''Journal of Health Politics, Policy and Law''''' is a bimonthly [[peer-review]]ed [[medical journal]] covering [[health policy]] and [[health law]] as they relate to [[politics]]. It was established in 1976 and is published by [[Duke University Press]]. The [[editor-in-chief]] is Eric M. Patashnik ([[Brown University]]). According to the ''[[Journal Citation Reports]]'', the journal had a 2014 [[impact factor]] of 1.373.<ref name=WoS>{{cite book |year=2015 |chapter=Journal of Health Politics, Policy and Law |title=2014 [[Journal Citation Reports]] |publisher=[[Thomson Reuters]] |edition=Science |series=[[Web of Science]]}}</ref>
